	<div id="contentwide">
    <h2>Biography</h2>
		<p>I am a Ph.D student in <a href="http://is.njit.edu" target="_blank">Information Systems</a> department of <a href="http://www.njit.edu" target="_blank">New Jersey Institute of Technology</a>.
			Recently, I am working with Prof. <a href="http://web.njit.edu/~ychen/" target="_blank">Yi Chen</a>.

		</p>
		<p>
			My research interests are broadly in <b>Natural Language Processing</b>, <b>Text Mining</b>, and <b>Computational Advertising</b>.
		My current projects are about <b>Ad Viewability Prediction</b> and <b>Short Text Classification</b>.
		</p>
    <p>
		<h3>[<a href="resume.pdf" target="_blank">Complete CV</a>]</h3>
	  </p>

